OL,3,CNHS cutting services and frontline
OL,4,Cclinical jobs, health leaders warn
OL,6,FNHS trusts are cutting frontline
OL,7,Fclinical jobs and axing patient
OL,8,Fservices to balance the books, health
OL,9,Fleaders have warned.
OL,11,FA survey of trust leaders by NHS
OL,12,FProviders found clinical jobs have
OL,13,Falready gone or are earmarked for
OL,14,Fcuts, while services such as virtual
OL,15,Fwards, diabetes clinics,
OL,16,Frehabilitation centres, talking
OL,17,Ftherapies and stop-smoking services
OL,18,Fare at risk or are being scaled back.
OL,20,FAt one NHS trust, 600 out of 1,500 job
OL,21,Fcuts are clinical roles.
