OL,3,CNHS cutting services and frontline
OL,4,Cclinical jobs, health leaders warn
OL,6,FAnother trust is cutting end-of-life
OL,7,Fand palliative care beds in the
OL,8,Fcommunity, restricting stop-smoking
OL,9,Fservices, and working to reduce
OL,10,Freferrals to hospital.
OL,12,FThe Providers' survey, which ran last
OL,13,Fmonth, included responses from 160 NHS
OL,14,Fchief executives, chairmen, and other
OL,15,Fboard executive directors. These cover
OL,16,F114 trusts in England and account for
OL,17,F56% of the sector.
OL,19,FThe poll found 47% of trust leaders
OL,20,Fare scaling back services, with a
OL,21,Ffurther 43% considering this option.
