OL,3,CNHS cutting services and frontline
OL,4,Cclinical jobs, health leaders warn
OL,6,FMore than one in four (26%) said they
OL,7,Fwill need to close some services and a
OL,8,Fthird (37%) said their organisation is
OL,9,Falso cutting clinical posts to balance
OL,10,Ftheir books.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, 86% of trust leaders said
OL,13,Ftheir organisation is also cutting
OL,14,Fposts in non-clinical teams ` such as
OL,15,FHR, finance, estates, digital and
OL,16,Fcommunications ` after being told to
OL,17,Fhalve corporate cost growth.
OL,19,FSeveral trusts said they were aiming
OL,20,Ffor reductions of 500 or more jobs.
