OL,11,FIn March, the then NHS chief Amanda
OL,12,FPritchard and Sir Jim Mackey, who is
OL,13,Fnow in charge of transition at NHS
OL,14,FEngland, wrote to trusts regarding the
OL,15,Fneed for cuts, saying there was a
OL,16,F"very significant financial deficit
OL,17,F(#6.6 billion when deficit support is
OL,18,Fstripped out)" and lack of confidence
OL,19,Fthat operational aims would be met.
