OL,6,FThe letter said: "We cannot allow this
OL,7,Fto continue and drift into the
OL,8,Ffinancial year, so we have been
OL,9,Fconsidering a fundamental reset of the
OL,10,Ffinancial regime and accountability so
OL,11,Fthat we can all, quickly, get a grip
OL,12,Fof this situation."
OL,14,FIn the Providers survey, 45% of
OL,15,Fleaders said they were moderately or
OL,16,Fextremely concerned the actions they
OL,17,Fwere taking to make savings would
OL,18,Fcompromise patient experience.
