OL,3,CNHS cutting services and frontline
OL,4,Cclinical jobs, health leaders warn
OL,6,FSome 61% said patient experience is
OL,7,Fmost at risk of being impacted by the
OL,8,Fchanges, 60% said addressing health
OL,9,Finequalities and 57% thought access to
OL,10,Ftimely care would take a hit.
OL,12,FNearly nine in 10 (88%) said they did
OL,13,Fnot have enough funding to invest in
OL,14,Fprevention of ill health ` one of the
OL,15,FGovernment's key aims.
OL,17,FOther cost-cutting measures
OL,18,Fhighlighted in the survey included
OL,19,Freductions on using agency staff and
OL,20,Frecruitment freezes.
