OL,3,CNHS cutting services and frontline
OL,4,Cclinical jobs, health leaders warn
OL,6,FMore than nine in 10 leaders (94%)
OL,7,Fsaid their plans would have a negative
OL,8,Fimpact on current staff wellbeing and
OL,9,Fthe culture of their organisation.
OL,11,FInterim chief executive of NHS
OL,12,FProviders, Saffron Cordery, said: "The
OL,13,FNHS has just undergone a significant
OL,14,Ffinancial reset in response to a
OL,15,Fdeficit that ran across the health and
OL,16,Fcare system of between #6 billion and
OL,17,F#7 billion.
OL,19,F"There was clearly a pressing need to
OL,20,Ftackle what was becoming a spiralling
OL,21,Fdeficit - an understandable deficit.
