OL,3,CNHS cutting services and frontline
OL,4,Cclinical jobs, health leaders warn
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokeswoman said: "We invested an
OL,8,Fextra #26 billion to fix the broken
OL,9,Fhealth and care system we inherited,
OL,10,Fand through our plan for change are
OL,11,Fdetermined to tackle inefficiencies
OL,12,Fand drive up productivity in the NHS.
OL,14,F"We have underlined the need for
OL,15,Ftrusts to cut bureaucracy to invest
OL,16,Feven further in the front line, so we
OL,17,Fcan support hard-working staff and
OL,18,Fdeliver a better service for patients
OL,19,Fand taxpayers' money."
